.000Z","msg":"又話得芯有毒，姐係點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:45:55.000Z","msg":"若熟食，每次20~30粒為宜，如去殼、去紅軟膜、去胚煮食，即使劑量大一些，也是不會發生中毒的。<br />\n<br />\n專家表示，白果不宜多吃，每次食用以10-20粒為宜，因為多吃可能會中毒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://read01.com/d47mo7.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2Fd47mo7.html&d=PjAGIXuhr%2FYv5tc13vOj90%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=e835aeaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/d47mo7.html</a>"},{"pid":"2ea159a2b29a5dd82650fca9d2afe84ea97514ff","tid":890582,"uid":41317,"like":2,"dislike":32,"score":-30,"quote":{"pid":"5fb6288d7214bfbbe9f14b180669e9adaec3f867","tid":890582,"uid":12021,"like":139,"dislike":1,"score":138,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:41:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:47:36.000Z","msg":"我喺舖頭買嗰啲炒完去殼去芯一包包pack好晒嚟賣嘅<br />\n啲小販檔唔做處理就咁賣, 咁係邊個問題"},{"pid":"e34df640bf2650f55defc2d23dc82fbb6f873689","tid":890582,"uid":19005,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:51:30.000Z","msg":"支那狗邊忽有腦食冇芯個白果<br />\n鬼國好撚多食物中毒新聞睇佢地一個唔出奇<br />\n死撚咪仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c75f775f7a7e64a6902e201c08d1cebb02372a","tid":890582,"uid":49197,"like":90,"dislike":2,"score":88,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:54:39.000Z","msg":"白果其實有咩好食<br />\n係買就買鵪鶉蛋/炒栗子啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0322b92153a31392b11b9c381bd4091c9bcb5bf","tid":890582,"uid":3302,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:56:28.000Z","msg":"刷首抽新方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1957e5b76cd7bb0f2200eadddf09ec0d497a3a4","tid":890582,"uid":113512,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:58:38.000Z","msg":"好少聽就咁食白果<br />\n通常都係煲湯煲糖水"},{"pid":"236f8624e624170233be75df7fda604e130ae533","tid":890582,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":21,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11