宜，如去殼、去紅軟膜、去胚煮食，即使劑量大一些，也是不會發生中毒的。<br />\n<br />\n專家表示，白果不宜多吃，每次食用以10-20粒為宜，因為多吃可能會中毒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://read01.com/d47mo7.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2Fd47mo7.html&d=PjAGIXuhr%2FYv5tc13vOj90%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=e835aeaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/d47mo7.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T14:35:44.000Z","msg":"你係咪戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有衛生署唔信走去quote Content Farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18bfd05d8e76970f4ba45592253e9b8d4b88f9bc","tid":890582,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23c609b3c5dcfd160a6cdaa1683a13c7c70d2e50","tid":890582,"uid":36432,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"8d09e2a9df03dbf59cb1aee1116d9e6eb90da585","tid":890582,"uid":531,"like":2,"dislike":35,"score":-33,"quote":{"pid":"4f6e5cde1ed452e3f9e0c3afb2d38c93b53c55fb","tid":890582,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:40:42.000Z","msg":"又話得芯有毒，姐係點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:45:55.000Z","msg":"若熟食，每次20~30粒為宜，如去殼、去紅軟膜、去胚煮食，即使劑量大一些，也是不會發生中毒的。<br />\n<br />\n專家表示，白果不宜多吃，每次食用以10-20粒為宜，因為多吃可能會中毒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://read01.com/d47mo7.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2Fd47mo7.html&d=PjAGIXuhr%2FYv5tc13vOj90%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=e835aeaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/d47mo7.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T14:35:44.000Z","msg":"你係咪戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有衛生署唔信走去quote Content Farm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T14:53:55.000Z","msg":"衞生署發言人解釋，天然毒素存在於多種植物內，當中有些是人們常吃的食物，包括白果，白果含有能主要影響神經系統的毒素。中白果毒的人通常在進食一至12小時後便會出現嘔吐、煩躁、持續或陣攣性抽搐等典型徵狀，這類食物中毒多見於兒童。嚴重中毒個案（即進食大量白果）的病人或易受白果毒素影響的人，可能會失去知覺，甚至死亡。<br />\n<br />\n發言人補充，曾有報告指出一次過進食10至50顆經煮熟的白果，可引致急性中毒。未成熟及未經煮熟的白果毒性更強，煮熟後毒性亦隨之減低。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e159bd752b9a5c9f2297d738c81e4d635f5432","tid":890582,"uid":178574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T15:02:59.000Z","msg":"正宗食白果..."},{"pid":"62952f2d0f2c77c4e6bcc86bf28457d626ecfc88","tid":890582,"uid":217728,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T15:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好癲 老實我都唔知"},{"pid":"71a595aa40ff2a0b462e010ca249634e49735797","tid":890582,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T15:12:41.000Z","msg":"平時食白果糖水都唔鐘意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a810a129104f19f21a552efa3468b94a970311c7","tid":890582,"uid":178228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T15:18:52.000Z","msg":"食白果自殺會飽死定毒死先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c77e924a4cad309127c955420d82887664917f","tid":890582,"uid":154255,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T15:32:03.000Z","msg":"on9 <br />\n平時我食幾十粒都無野<br />\n飲糖水至少都食20粒啦 咁好食<br />\n無煮熟姐"},{"pid":"d92f6105126aea5713d1a98fda722299ad12f6dc","tid":890582,"uid":103347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T15:37:50.000Z","msg":"熱刺球迷？"}]}